Hey my dear community! {{champion:36}} 
I&#039;ve been playing in OCE for three years already since I moved to Australia. I&#039;m from South America so I used to play in Latin America North (LAN). But when I first transferred my account to OCE I realised that the direct transfers from LAN to OCE are unavailable {{summoner:3}} {{champion:32}} This makes me very sad because I travel constantly back home for a couple months to visit my family but I still live in Australia so my solution is to transfer my account constantly to keep enjoying the summoners rift at its most! 
I would like to know if theres any chance that in the future you guys open the direct account trasnfers from LAN to OCE since i find it quite unfair that theres so many posibilities of transfer (Including OCE to LAN) but the option from LAN to OCE is not available {{item:3073}} 
I hope you consider my request!
Thank you and have a great day {{summoner:31}}
